segment.source: Use the following list of errors to identify the reasons why command-line sequencing is not working properly.
segment.target: Use the following list of errors to identify the reasons why command-line sequencing is not working properly.

segment.source: You can also see these errors by viewing the sequencer log file.
segment.target: You can also see these errors by viewing the sequencer log file.

segment.source: Note
segment.target: Note

segment.source: More than one error might be displayed when sequencing.
segment.target: More than one error might be displayed when sequencing.

segment.source: Furthermore, the error code displayed might be the sum of two error codes.
segment.target: Furthermore, the error code displayed might be the sum of two error codes.

segment.source: For example, if the /InstallPath and /OutputFile parameters are missing, the Microsoft System Center Application Virtualization Sequencer will return 96—the sum of the two error codes.
segment.target: For example, if the /InstallPath and /OutputFile parameters are missing, the Microsoft System Center Application Virtualization Sequencer will return 96—the sum of the two error codes.
